name: GetFinancialBudgets
description:
Fetch financial budgets for organizations.

Use this tool to retrieve financial budget data for specified organizations through the Entrata service. Supports pagination for large data sets.

parameters.name: client_subdomain
parameters.description: The subdomain of the client organization for which to fetch financial budgets.

parameters.name: ar_payment_requests
parameters.description: A list of JSON objects representing AR payment related data for processing. Each JSON object should contain details as required by the specific AR payment APIs.

metadata.description: Tools that enable LLMs to interact directly with the Entrata API
